All Implemented Interfaces:
net.sf.saxon.expr.StaticContext
public class AeXQueryStaticQueryContext
extends net.sf.saxon.query.StaticQueryContext

A simple class used during static XQuery expression syntax validation. This class is necessary to resolve unknown prefixes to their corresponding namespaces. For static syntax validation, it is not important what the prefix maps to, as long as it maps to something. The resulting resolved URI will then be passed into the function library to bind a prefixed function to a function impl.
